Hi, so in the past weeks I noticed I've had neither the temporal nor the mental capacity to work on clippy, I didn't even find motivation to finish my pr recently, so it's probably best for me to take a break from the project right now.
I hope I'll find motivation again at some future point in time.
I'll take care of the PRs assigned to you and will look at finishing your improvement of single_char_push_str. Now take some time for yourself!
@matthiaskrgr could you remove yourself from highfive rotation? Otherwise I have 2x chance to review :sweat_smile:
